                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3757" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0170</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8316 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“上”“下”求索：传统制造企业LN船厂的信息化升级之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Research from ‘top’ to ‘bottom’: The Way to Informationization Upgrade of LN Shipyard in Traditional Manufacturing Enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">薄洪光，张慧琳，李焕之</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连辽南船厂</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">制造型企业；两化融合；车间制造执行系统；业务流程优化 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> manufacturing enterprises, optimization and construction of integration of information and industrialization, manufacturing execution system, business process improvement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">制造业属于国民经济的基础，是一个国家保持长久发展的根基。LN船厂作为传统的船舶制造企业，为了响应国家号召，已经进行了10多年的信息化建设。但随着市场经济的深入发展和客户需求的不断变化，业务部门在实际的生产工作与管理工作中均出现了不同程度的问题。本案例描述了LN船厂在新形势新背景下融合信息化技术，推动管理模式及研发流程的深刻变革，实现工厂的转型升级。在本案例中，通过分析原有信息化工程出现的问题与业务部门当前的需求，对比旧新旧信息化建设工程内容，发现并展示传统中小型制造业企业在信息化建设过程中容易遇到的难点与忽略的问题，为找到实现制造型企业两化融合体系的合理化、针对性解决方案提供了思路。同时，通过本案例让学生们了解到在“信息化之风”盛行的当下，仍然有许多本土制造型企业需要合理且有效的手段促使企业快速转型，适应发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The manufacturing industry is the foundation of the national economy for its long-term development. LN Shipyard, as a traditional shipbuilding enterprise, has experienced more than 10 years of informationalized construction for the call of the State. However, with the further development of market economy and the continuous change of customer demands, the departments of LN shipyard have different problems in the actual production and management work. This case describes LN Shipyard&#39;s integration of information technology under the new conditions, promoting profound changes in management modes and R&amp;D process, and realizing the transformation and upgrading of the factory. In this case, by analyzing the existing problems and the current needs of business departments, and comparing the contents of different construction projects, we find and show the difficulties and neglected problems that traditional manufacturing enterprises are likely to encounter in the process of informationalized construction. And a rational and targeted solution for realizing the integration system of manufacturing enterprises is provided. Meanwhile, this case lets students know that there are still many local manufacturing enterprises need reasonable and effective means to promote the rapid transformation of enterprises and adapt to development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业资源管理与信息化》、《生产运作管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">两化融合体系；企业资源计划；车间制造执行系统；业务流程优化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
